mmary Report</li><li>Bank Payment Sheet</li><li>Envelope Report (EOT)</li><li>Worker Salary Sheet</li><li>Staff Salary Sheet</li><li>Grade Wise Summary</li><li>Pay Slip</li><li>Provident Fund</li><li>Max-Min OT Sheet</li><li>Actual Salary Sheet</li><li>Actual Salary Sheet with EOT</li><li>Max-Min EOT Sheet</li><li>Monthly EOT Sheet</li><li>Envelope Report</li><li>Salary Sheet &amp; OT</li><li>F-H OT Sheet</li></ul></li><li><strong>Percentage Salary Reports</strong><ul><li>Total Percent Salary</li><li>Total Fraction Salary</li><li>Gross Percent Salary</li><li>Gross Fraction Salary</li><li>Total Percent Summary</li></ul></li><li><strong>Others Benefit Report</strong><ul><li>Maternity Benefit Report</li><li>Festival Bonus</li><li>Advance Salary Sheet</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li>Maintenance: Maintenance of the system<ul><li>Database:<ul><li>Backup: Database Backup for any occurrence.</li></ul></li><li>User<ul><li>ACL: Create new Users and define roll for the user.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '73', 'mysoftheavenbd, ERP, ERP software, Sheba ERP,  Best  ERP system in Dhaka,  SHEBA ERP System', 'SHEBA ERP System of Mysoft Heaven BD Ltd is the best ERP system in Dhaka for maintaining your total organization tasks and a complete Enterprise Resource Planning System.', 'http://173.212.223.213/erp', 10, 1, 1),
(2, '', 'HR Sheba | Best HR Software in Bangladesh', 'best-hr-software-in-bangladesh', '438231103_374761272223436_6091012394832469885_n.jpg', '<h2><strong>Best HR Software in Bangladesh – Complete HRM, Payroll, and Attendance Solution</strong></h2><p>Looking for the <strong>Best HR Software in Bangladesh</strong> to simplify and automate your human resources operations? Our all-in-one HR management platform is built to streamline every step of the employee lifecycle—from hiring to retirement—while ensuring full compliance with local labor laws.</p><p>This comprehensive HR system integrates <strong>Time Attendance</strong>, <strong>HRM</strong>, and <strong>Payroll</strong> into one seamless solution. Whether you\'re managing a factory floor or an office-based team, our software adapts to your organizational needs, supporting both <strong>compliance</strong> and <strong>non-compliance</strong> setups.</p><h3><strong>Core Modules</strong></h3><p><strong>Hiring &amp; Recruiting</strong></p><p>Dynamic onboarding for new employees with detailed info capture</p><p>Zoning and departmental assignments</p><p>Resume tracking, background checks, nominee details</p><p><strong>Retaining &amp; HR Planning</strong></p><p>Promotion &amp; increment management</p><p>Training and learning module</p><p>Performance tracking and appraisal support</p><p>Earn Leave calculation and automation</p><p><strong>Administration</strong></p><p>Department, designation, and zone setup</p><p>Dynamic relations and positions management</p><p>Centralized data for employee lifecycle</p><p><strong>Payroll Management</strong></p><p>Automated monthly salary process (single &amp; batch)</p><p>Allowance, bonus, PF, EOT, and OT integration</p><p>Bank payment reports, payslips, salary sheets</p><p>Festival and maternity bonus modules</p><p><strong>Attendance &amp; Scheduling</strong></p><p>Shift creation &amp; management</p><p>Daily, weekly, and monthly attendance tracking</p><p>OT, late arrival, out punch, and early leave reports</p><p>Gate pass, lunch punch, and manual entry support</p><p><strong>Absence Management</strong></p><p>Leave setup and approval workflow</p><p>Leave balance reports and deletion history</p><p>Earned leave and short leave tracking</p><p><strong>Performance Records</strong></p><p>Increment, promotion, and performance history</p><p>Length of service reports</p><p>Appraisal documents and NOC letter generation</p><h3><strong>Main Sub-Modules</strong></h3><h4>1. <strong>Time Attendance</strong></h4><p>Daily attendance, punch reports, out punch missing</p><p>OT, EOT, and lunch break tracking</p><p>Actual present vs reported present reports</p><p>Gate pass, short leave, holiday/weekend delete</p><h4>2. <strong>HRM</strong></h4><p>Employee information with complete history</p><p>Dynamic setups for zone, floor, shift, designation</p><p>Manual attendance entries, resignation and separation records</p><p>Filtering &amp; searching across all employee records</p><h4>3. <strong>Payroll</strong></h4><p>Single &amp; multiple salary processing</p><p>Grade-wise summary, staff &amp; worker sheets</p><p>Envelope, payslip, and actual salary reports</p><p>PF interest entry, advance salary, loan deduction</p><p>Festival bonus and maternity benefit tracking</p><h3><strong>Reporting System</strong></h3><p>Our HR software offers <strong>over 50+ dynamic reports</strong> for better visibility and decision-making:</p><p><strong>Daily Reports:</strong> Present, absent, late, OT, IN/OUT, lunch punch</p><p><strong>Monthly Reports:</strong> Salary, attendance, EOT, increment/promotion letters</p><p><strong>Continuous Reports:</strong> Cross-period trends on performance and attendance</p><p><strong>Special Reports:</strong> ID Cards, NOC Letters, App Letters, Job Cards, Zone-based reports</p><p>All reports come with advanced <strong>filtering and export options</strong> to ensure you get the insights you need—fast.</p><h3><strong>Security &amp; Maintenance</strong></h3><p><strong>User Access Control (ACL):</strong> Assign specific roles to each user</p><p><strong>Database Backup:</strong> Regular and on-demand backups ensure data integrity</p><p><strong>Maintenance Tools:</strong> Easily maintain system data and configurations</p><h3>Why This is the <strong>Best HR Software in Bangladesh</strong></h3><p>Covers <strong>complete employee lifecycle</strong></p><p>Supports both <strong>compliant and non-compliant payroll</strong></p><p>Built with <strong>factory and corporate HR needs</strong> in mind</p><p>Highly <strong>customizable and dynamic</strong></p><p>Robust <strong>data security and user management</strong></p><p>50+ detailed <strong>reports &amp; analytics</strong></p><p>Proven to <strong>save time, reduce errors, and boost HR efficiency</strong></p><p>If you\'re searching for the <strong>Best HR Software in Bangladesh</strong>, this solution offers the perfect balance of flexibility, compliance, and automation to meet your organization’s growing HR and payroll needs.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2><h3>1. <strong>What makes this the Best HR Software in Bangladesh?</strong></h3><p>Our HR software stands out for its <strong>comprehensive coverage</strong> of HRM, Time Attendance, and Payroll—all in one system. It’s fully customizable, supports both <strong>compliance and non-compliance</strong> environments, and offers 50+ reports to help businesses make data-driven HR decisions.</p><h3>2. <strong>What industries is this HR software suitable for?</strong></h3><p>It’s designed to serve both <strong>factory-based and corporate organizations</strong>, including garments/textiles, manufacturing, logistics, and service-based sectors. The dynamic setup options (e.g., zoning, shifts, floors) make it highly flexible.</p><h3>3. <strong>Does the software support attendance with biometric devices?</strong></h3><p>Yes, the system can be integrated with <strong>biometric or RFID attendance devices</strong> to automate employee attendance tracking. It also supports <strong>manual entries</strong> for adjustments when needed.</p><h3>4. <strong>Can we manage payroll and bonuses automatically?</strong></h3><p>Absolutely. Our payroll module includes:</p><p><strong>Auto salary processing</strong> (single or multiple)</p><p><strong>Festival bonus</strong>, <strong>maternity benefit</strong>, and <strong>advance salary</strong></p><p>Full <strong>bank payment and payslip generation</strong></p><p><strong>Grade-wise salary sheets</strong> and <strong>EOT/OT tracking</strong></p><h3>5. <strong>Is this HR software compliant with Bangladeshi labor laws?</strong></h3><p>Yes. The system is built to handle both <strong>compliant and non-compliant HR practices</strong>, so it can adapt to your internal policy and meet <strong>legal and regulatory standards</strong> in Bangladesh.</p><h3>6. <strong>How does Earned Leave calculation work?</strong></h3><p>Earned Leave is calculated using a dynamic rule:<br><strong>Earned Leave = (Total working days in a year ÷ 18) × (Monthly salary ÷ 30)</strong><br>This can be customized per company policy and is reflected in both leave balance and payroll.</p><h3>7. <strong>Can I track employee performance and promotions?</strong></h3><p>Yes. The system allows:</p><p><strong>Increment and promotion entries</strong></p><p><strong>Performance history tracking</strong></p><p>Monthly letters and reports for both activities</p><h3>8. <strong>Is there any report filtering option?</strong></h3><p>Yes. Every report (daily, monthly, attendance, payroll, etc.) has <strong>advanced filtering</strong> based on department, zone, designation, employee status, and more.</p><h3>9. <strong>Is the system cloud-based or on-premise?</strong></h3><p>We support both <strong>cloud-hosted</strong> and <strong>on-premise</strong> deployments based on your infrastructure preference and data security requirements.</p><h3>10. <strong>How is data backed up and secured?</strong></h3><p>The system includes:</p><p><strong>Automatic and manual database backup</strong></p><p><strong>Role-based access control (ACL)</strong></p><p><strong>User management</strong> to control who sees what</p><p>Secure login and data encryption (optional for cloud)</p><h3>11. <strong>Can I create ID cards, NOC letters, and job cards?</strong></h3><p>Yes. The system includes ready templates to generate:</p><p><strong>ID cards</strong> (Bangla &amp; English)</p><p><strong>Job cards</strong>, <strong>appointment letters</strong>, and <strong>NOC documents</strong></p><p><strong>Nominee reports</strong> and <strong>resume tracking</strong></p><h3>12. <strong>How many users can access the system?</strong></h3><p>There’s <strong>no limit</strong> to the number of users. Admins can define roles and permissions through the <strong>ACL (Access Control List)</strong> module.</p>', '<ol><li>Retaining</li><li>Hiring</li><li>Administration</li><li>Managing Payroll</li><li>HR planning</li><li>Recruiting/Learning management</li><li>Performance record</li><li>Scheduling</li><li>Absence management</li></ol>', '<p><strong>This systems is Compliance &amp; None Compliance</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;Three main Sub-Modules. 1) Time Attendance 2) HRM &amp; 3) Payroll</strong></p><ul><li>HRM<ul><li>Employee Info: New Employee joining with all basic information &amp; Zooning.</li><li>Setup:&nbsp; All Setup is Dynamic. There are:-<ul><li>Company Information</li><li>Relation</li><li>Department</li><li>Section</li><li>Line</li><li>Designation</li><li>Position</li><li>Operation</li><li>Zone</li><li>Floor</li><li>Salary Grade</li><li>Shift Schedules</li><li>Shift Manage</li><li>Leave Setup</li><li>Attendance Bonus</li><li>Bonus Setup</li><li>Allowance Setup</li><li>Provident Setup</li></ul></li><li>Entry System<ul><li>All Entry:&nbsp; Entry Manual Attendance, Present to Absent, Weekend, Holiday</li><li>Leave Transaction: Leave Transaction with search leave balance</li><li>Advance Loan:&nbsp; Any Employee get