ess with single &amp; multiple.</li></ul></li><li>Reports<ul><li>Salary Report<ul><li>Manual Salary Sheet</li><li>Salary Summary Report</li><li>Bank Payment Sheet</li><li>Envelope Report (EOT)</li><li>Worker Salary Sheet</li><li>Staff Salary Sheet</li><li>Grade Wise Summary</li><li>Pay Slip</li><li>Provident Fund</li><li>Max-Min OT Sheet</li><li>Actual Salary Sheet</li><li>Actual Salary Sheet with EOT</li><li>Max-Min EOT Sheet</li><li>Monthly EOT Sheet</li><li>Envelope Report</li><li>Salary Sheet &amp; OT</li><li>F-H OT Sheet</li></ul></li><li><strong>Percentage Salary Reports</strong><ul><li>Total Percent Salary</li><li>Total Fraction Salary</li><li>Gross Percent Salary</li><li>Gross Fraction Salary</li><li>Total Percent Summary</li></ul></li><li><strong>Others Benefit Report</strong><ul><li>Maternity Benefit Report</li><li>Festival Bonus</li><li>Advance Salary Sheet</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li>Maintenance: Maintenance of the system<ul><li>Database:<ul><li>Backup: Database Backup for any occurrence.</li></ul></li><li>User<ul><li>ACL: Create new Users and define roll for the user.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '7', 'Best HR Software in Bangladesh', 'Best HR Software in Bangladesh for payroll, attendance & HRM. Fully compliant, customizable & ideal for factories, corporates & growing teams.', 'http://173.212.223.213/hrshebahttp://173.212.223.213/hrsheba', 20, 1, 1),
(3, '', 'Salesman | Point of Sales', 'salesman', 'WhatsApp_Image_2024-10-30_at_12_28_19_PM.jpeg', '<p>Point of sales is the zone of bill payment by the customer to salesman and &nbsp;Salesman app is here to minimize the harassments of the billing system.</p><p><strong>Salesman Software</strong></p><p>Point of sale (POS) is that the time and place wherever a retail dealing is completed by “Salesman” software package. At the purpose of sale, the worker calculates the quantity owed by the client, indicates that quantity, might prepare associate degree invoice for the client and indicates the choices for the customer to make payment. It is also the point at which a customer makes a payment to the employee in exchange for goods or after the provision of a service. After receiving payment, the employee may issue a receipt for the transaction, which is usually printed with the help of a printer but is increasingly being dispensed with or sent electronically.</p><p><strong>Why do you need a \"Salesman\" Software?</strong></p><p>To calculate the amount owed by a customer, the employee may use various devices such as weighing scales, barcode scanners, and cash registers. To make a payment, payment terminals, touch screens, other hardware and software options are available along with that software. Its work for management and control, Customer relationship management, financials, or warehousing.</p><p>Businesses are increasingly adopting Salesman (POS) systems, and one of the most obvious and compelling reasons is that a “Salesman” (POS) system does away with the need for price tags. When you want to add stock then you should be linked to the product code with selling prices. So, the cashier simply needs to scan the product code to process any kinds of sale. Price up down is a normal nature of the market, If there is a major price change in the market then this can easily be solved by the inventory window. This software includes various advantages likeability of implication types of discount, goodwill scheme for customers, and increase efficiency in stock control.</p><p>as it is the most sensitive section of any kind of transaction this should be pampered in best way and Salesman app is the <a href=\"http://mysoftheaven.com/service/integrated-office-management-system\"><i><strong>best POS software</strong></i></a> for you.&nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Setup</li><li>Sale</li><li>Inventory</li><li>Customer</li><li>Reports</li><li>DB Backup</li><li>Supplier</li><li>Accounts</li><li>Logout</li></ul>', '<ol><li><strong>Setup:</strong> Enables user to enter detail information of the below listed functions. All information regarding establishment of the POS (Point of Sale) System is provided in this section.</li></ol><ul><li>Item Setup</li><li>Unit Setup</li><li>Shop</li><li>Employee</li><li>Company</li><li>ACL</li><li>ACL Group</li><li>Password</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Sale: </strong>In this section, the products and sold product are returned here</li></ol><ul><li>Sale</li><li>Return Sale</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Inventory:</strong> Enables user to enter the below listed functions.</li></ol><ul><li>Add Item</li><li>Damage Item</li><li>Barcode</li><li>Purchase Order</li><li>Purchase Receive</li><li>Category</li><li>Subcategory</li><li>Loan</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Customer:</strong> Here user’s can enter detail information of the below listed functions.</li></ol><ul><li>Customers</li><li>Due Packages</li><li>Due Payment</li><li>Due Setup</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Reports:</strong> All Report has filtering.</li><li><strong>Sales Report</strong></li><li><strong>Date Mode </strong>(here at first, you have to select the date)</li></ol><ul><li>Summary</li><li>Detailed</li><li>Summary Transaction</li><li>Detailed Transaction</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Customer Mode </strong>(here at first, you have to select the customer name or id)</li></ol><ul><li>Summary</li><li>Detailed</li><li>Summary Transaction</li><li>Detailed Transaction</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Item M