Summary Re. Trans.</li><li>Detail Re. Trans.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li><strong>Item Mode</strong></li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Summary Loan</li><li>Detail Loan</li><li>Summary Loan Return</li><li>Detail Loan Return</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Transaction Mode</strong></li></ol><ul><li>Summary Transaction Loan</li><li>Detail Transaction Loan</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Database Backup:</strong> Enables user to create database backup.</li></ol><ul><li>DB Backup</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Supplier:</strong> Enables user to enter the below listed functions regarding supplier information.</li></ol><ul><li>Add Supplier</li><li>Due Payments</li><li>Suppliers Item</li><li>Item Return</li></ul><ol><li>Accounts: Enables user to select different payment option.</li></ol><ul><li>Payments Type</li></ul><ol><li><strong>Log Out</strong></li></ol>', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '7', 'salesman, salesman apps, POS, point of sales,  best POS software firm in Dhaka,', 'Point of sales is the zone of bill payment by the customer to salesman and  Salesman app is here to minimize the harassments of the billing system.', 'http://173.212.223.213/Salesman', 50, 1, 1),
(4, '', 'Binyog | Leading Investment  Management Software', 'binyog', 'Binyog.png', '<p>Biniyog is the complete Multipurpose Management system to secure your investment return.&nbsp; This Multipurpose management system control your investment system to get the best return.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Biniyog Software</strong></p><p>Biniyog is the leading investment management software gives you real-time investment management analytics and data to help improve decision making. Front to back, our product portfolio convey the resources you need to superintend and optimize your investment staging and increase your operational alertness.</p><p><strong>The best investment portfolio management services:</strong></p><p>The list is long and I will start with the boring, yet politically correct answer “it depends”. It depends on what are your expectations vs. what the service can offer you. Now for the more practical, actionable part of the answer, there are a couple of ways to decide:</p><ul><li><strong>You\'ll attempt a DIY investment approach:&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><p>Open an occasional value, no minimum brokerage account and buy/sell stocks, ETFs and be your own portfolio manager. You have several choices: Interactive Brokers, Fidelity, Schwab, Scottrade, etc</p><ul><li><strong>Come with a monetary advisor:&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><p>Somebody World Health Organization can hear all of your wants, propose a plan and also implement it for you if you want. Financial advisors typically charge a heavy fee and work with certain minimums. They can charge a flat fee or hourly fee or realize ways that to charge you for his or her services in alternative ways that.</p><ul><li><strong>Go along with a digital advisor:&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><p>This business is new and still proving itself. There square measure already over 100+ digital advisors out there. They generally have a straightforward onboarding method, manage your account online and keep the method fairly clear. Not all Robo-advisors are the same but the good thing is that they are probably more heavily reviewed on the internet than most human advisors.</p><p>So take your&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mysoftheaven.com/service/support-maintenance-service\"><i><strong>best&nbsp;Multipurpose Management system</strong></i></a> for your investment now..&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '7', 'Biniyog, Leading Investment  Management, Multipurpose Management system,  Software, best investment portfolio management services,  mysoft Multipurpose system, multipurpose system', 'Biniyog is the complete Multipurpose Management system to secure your investment return. ', 'http://173.212.223.213/Multi Purpose', 70, 1, 1),
(5, '', 'Filling Master (ফিলিং মাস্টার)', 'filling-master', 'Filling_Master.png', '<p><strong>Filling Master Software</strong></p><p>A petrol pump management software is actually designed for a petroleum pump owner or Associate in nursing enterpriser running a petroleum pump business. The computer code can even be effectively employed by a petroleum pump chain. The options to seem for within the code area unit Meter reading, DIP readings, density, periodic credit request system, running short credit, counter charge, SMS facilities, fuel purchase with tanker details, card sales &amp; loading options, full financial accounting, inventory management, value-added tax integration, shift wise report, salesman wise reports, bank reconciliation, provisional entries, self-reminders, payroll with attendance, asset management, tanker trip entries and reports, evaporation entry, stock short access entry, fast dip enquiry, denomination entry, fuel sampling stickers, debtors management, meter &amp; MPD allotment to salesperson, zooming options, expense budgeting, stock inspection, sales target, multi stock point option, cheque printing provision, pay-in-slip printing, tally export module, analysis and reports, and more.</p><p>Any petrol pump station gets the best result from \"Filling Master\" software which is developed by the Mysoftheaven (BD) Ltd. We more than 17 years of experience in this field. The company caters to over 100+ clients across the country. The GST-ready hydrocarbon pump management software system designed by the corporate helps in managing charge and accounting in conjunction with trailing fuel variation standing. Owing to its good support and service, the company enjoys pan all over the country presence.</p><p><strong>Why do you need “Filling Master” software?</strong></p><p><strong>=&gt; Reduce Fuel Theft &amp; Fraud:</strong>&nbsp;Fuel felony and fraud aren’t new the fleet trade. You have to ensure that employees are adding the correct amount of fuel to vehicles. With the employment of a petroleum pump management software system, you\'ll stop any unauthorized use of fuel. In addition to that, the software system provides restricted access to hydrocarbon pump operators and thereby, facilitating simple chase of fuel consumption. Further, the cases of fuel fraud and abuse are prevented by monitoring fuel shrinkage with the help of a meter reading system. A petrol pump software system conjointly assists in fuel tanker watching and chase the precise quantity of fuel dud at your fuel station.</p><p><strong>=&gt; Billing &amp; Accounting:</strong>&nbsp;At hydrocarbon pump stations, the menu features a heap of tasks to manage together with invoicing. With so much to take care of, there is always some room for error when it comes to manual calculations. Additionally, human error could occur due to a lack of expertise or technical knowledge. However, of these problems square measure overruled once a petroleum pump management software system comes into the image. The software helps in generating invoices, Callan information, and maintaining the sale/purchase register.</p><p>Software like Petro Genius comes with an intensive ‘Accounts’ module and works sort of a real accounting software system. From passing the journal entry to generating financial statements, doing bank reconciliation, and maintaining trial balance, every accounting task is made easy and error-free with this petrol pump software.</p><p><strong>=&gt; Inventory Management:</strong>&nbsp;Lack of inventory management is one of the reasons behind fuel loss. When fuel tanker unloads, maintaining a correct record of the stock level is necessary to make sure you get what you have got received. And a petroleum pump management software system permits you to strictly monitor the fuel stock from the purpose it\'s received. Moreover, with automatic generation of reports like the stock outline and ledger maintenance, missing on one fuel drop is tough. Software like Petro Genius provides you with a stock report on day, value and month basis and therefore, you can keep tabs on every drop. In addition to it, the software gives you a reminder in case the quantity of stock is below the re-order level. Beside hydrocarbon, if a petrol station sells snacks and other items, the software facilitates the management of all such items.</p><p><strong>=&gt; Go Green:</strong>&nbsp;The hydrocarbon pump management software system not solely helps your business by rising its potency however conjointly the surroundings. Obtaining Pollution under Control certificate is a statutory requirement as per some states in the country. A petrol pump software system helps to keep a check on the expiration date of pollution certificate for all customers.</p><p><strong>=&gt; Report Generation:</strong>&nbsp;Petrol pump management software system helps with automatic report generation on client name, purchase, sales, stock, and other parameters. Further, the issue of reconciling physical stock with books will be resolved in no time.</p><p><strong>=&gt; Sales Management:</strong>&nbsp;Patrol Pump software helps in managing accounts, inventory, and sale. By generating sale reports and sale registers Callan wise, this system helps in effectively trailing your sales. Another is credit bills and outstanding payment management feature where bill by bill outstanding report is generated for your sales analysis.<br>So, if you\'re confused concerning managing your hydrocarbon pump, try your hands at petrol pump management software. There is plenty to be done at a petroleum station and also the software system will assist you in its overall management.</p>', '', '', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr>