(7, '', 'Gym Master (জিম মাস্টার)', 'gym-master', 'Gym_Master.png', '<p><strong>\"Gym Master Software\"</strong></p><p>Gym Master is gym management software designed to easily maintain of detailed records of your members, different packages, trainers, process and track sales, communicate with the right members at the right time and growth of your club. You can manage your body by maintaining and hard work in the gym and proper management help the company to make a good profit as well, so Mysoftheaven (BD) Ltd. Combined two theory in a row and after a certain period of research, we make Gym master&nbsp;software to ease the hassle of gym management.</p><p>A gym needs this software to operate plainly without causing unnecessary stress. You have to focus on many aspects like member satisfaction, manage their routine and give the effort to maintain trainer, billing procedure. Goodwill comes after good management and updates all of your facility, Gym Master help you to do all of this with a click.</p><p><strong>Why do you need to use Gym Master Software?</strong></p><p>If you plan to run a gym smoothly then you must use gym management software for better performance. This software will take care of different business operation as well with this dynamic quality.</p><ul><li><strong>Package management:</strong></li></ul><p>Every gym has different packages like gold, silver, platinum according to owner choice and he allocates all the information here including price. Every day like 100 people join your gym but you don\'t recognize that who is under which package. Here is the solution, Gym Master, you write someone name in the search bar when you see the whole package system, his due, performance, presence ratio. You don\'t need any paperwork for this just type the name and get all the information that you need.</p><ul><li><strong>Membership management:</strong></li></ul><p>Member tracking of your business is so important. You can easily track your member with gym management software including member list, add a new member. It can help with member check-ins, offering access to the member portal and adding in member information. With this software, you can easily add some new member information, pay the bills, schedule appointments, change gym timings.</p><ul><li><strong>Easy to payment process:</strong></li></ul><p>A gym is a client based business when a member selects a package then he or she might in the payment system. There is a different system of payments like yearly, half-yearly, monthly. The gym owner selects the payment option when one member joins this gym. Gym Master Keep owner always tension free, POS is another thing that comes with software and it handles electronic down payments and waivers. When the date expires of payment then automatically give a text to the member to remind him/her about payment. The proprietor can also add a new member for payment dynamically. It will also handle any kinds of billing of owner and others as kind of financial transactions.</p><ul><li><strong>Product management:</strong></li></ul><p>A gym has much product like home gym equipment, strength training workout equipment, home exercise machine resistance, weight training exercise workout equipment, strength machine fitness, etc. The owner has to maintain his/her asset. Gym Master Software has the option to keep track on it and add another product whatever employer want to add.</p><ul><li><strong>Saves your money and time:</strong></li></ul><p>Everyone tries to save their time and money and want to their work more enjoyable. The manual task is so boring, it also takes much time and you have also recruited a person for this job. It’s time to make the change and With Gym Master, your gym can become more profitable by automating tasks such as Reporting, Collecting dues, Schedule Management, Member Check-ins.</p><ul><li><strong>Reporting and Analysis tool:</strong></li></ul><p>Gym Master Software will offer reports which are valuable to use and track. Some of the reports you can generate are class attendance, billing statements, invoices, revenue per client, churn rate and account deposit summaries. Based on the collected information, it becomes easy for gym owners to make future decisions for the gym and manage cash flows.</p><p><strong>Mysoftheaven (BD) Ltd.</strong> Give attention to gym owner to buy Gym Master Software from us and make your business large with it. If you wish to build gym management software with all the right features and specifications.</p><p><strong>Why choose us?</strong></p><p>• We delivered the Gym Master 30+ Gym in Bangladesh and they are satisfied with our services. Their satisfaction level is 99% because we keep our promise to give the best service.</p><p>• Providing the latest technology and upgrade version of Gym Master. We will give a 3-month free service after buying our software.</p><p>• Gym Master is extremely user-friendly, don’t need extensive training and easy to navigate.</p><p>• Gym Master offers a cloud-based gym management software that is securely accessible from anywhere.</p><p>• We take your Gym management headache, for this reason, we complete all software setup and for the user, we give special free training sessions.</p><p>• We use the excellent server for backup your all information.</p><p>• Gym Master is a product that is constantly being updated based on data-driven by our customers and their feedback.</p><p>• Accept payment globally, with this feature you can send invoices quickly and can provide an awesome experience to the payee.</p><p>• Your data is the key to your business and this data is secured with hassle-free cloud computing.</p><p>• 24/7 support system and provide secured management whereas we know your information is valuable for your business.</p>', '', '', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 'gym master, physical fitness', 'A complete Gym Management system.', NULL, 90, 1, 1),
(8, '', 'Sompod - (সম্পদ) | Best Store Management system.', 'sompod', 'Sompod.png', '<p>Sompod | A complete Inventory/Best Store Management system for managing your inventory product and also things of your store brought by &nbsp;Mysoftheaven BD Ltd.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>\'Sompod\' Inventory management software</strong></p><p>Inventory management software (Sompod) is a system for tracking inventory levels, orders, sales, and deliveries. It is not only used in the manufacturing industry but also in larger companies. Inventory management usually helps you to manage your sales, purchasing, operations, inventory &amp;amp; basic accounting process.</p><p>\"Sompod\" software system will facilitate to optimize retailer’s warehouses and every one style of distributors, grovelers, artificers. More confidence in inventory accuracy will lead to a new focus on optimizing, expanding a selection and accelerating inventory turns. It is the means that by that corporations stay furnished all of the essential merchandise they have to sell to customers and complete daily operations. When product square measure sold, they must be replenished at a rate that doesn’t lead to huge overstocks or frequent stock-outs.</p><p>It has great power to manage your effort from sales, purchasing and delivery with stock, accounting, shipping and customer data from a single place. It also helps the business to track customer payment, detailed selling price, costing, deal margins, inventory valuation and movement. Product Catalog management. Improve internal control through mechanically updated stock levels whenever sales and purchases square measure created.</p><p><strong>Why do you need to use inventory management?</strong></p><p>Inventory management is very important to manage a business and stock management software solves it smoothly. If you are looking to manage, monitor and correction of your inventory then you should choose “Sompod” software because it is the right fit of your business. Here is some elaboration part of choose Sompod software:</p><ul><li><strong>Stock management:</strong></li></ul><p>The key feature of this system is stock management. Managing a large number of items is a critical requirement of any business. This inventory management software provides many intuitional ways of managing, tracking and correcting your stock. With this Sompod Software, you can regularly track and correct your physical stock to match with your database. It also takes care of damages, dumps happening in your stock.</p><ul><li><strong>Stock Audit:</strong></li></ul><p>Inventory control system generates complete audit of any stock, change in the system. This inventory monitoring software provides you various ways to identify the mismatch if any between your physical stock and your stock in the database. You can do this stock monitoring on smaller chunks of your inventory so that during stock validation you do not need to disturb your daily billing operations. This store inventory software also supports stock validation using excel files generated by many industry-standard wireless handheld barcode scanners.</p><ul><li><strong>Handle multiple warehouses:</strong></li></ul><p>This system increases your organization\'s ability to manage your inventory at various warehouses. It allows you to the specific physical location of each item at each warehouse. This warehouse Inventory management software provides you with easy ways to move stock from one warehouse to another with a complete audit trail.</p><ul><li><strong>Expiration management:</strong></li></ul><p>When you are in business to sell goods that expire over some time and you can return near expiring goods back to the supplier, management of expiration dates become critical for you. Sompod software is the complete inventory management system that also keeps track of your batch numbers and their corresponding expiration dates. You can query this software any time to find all near expiring goods and create a purchase return for them. Essentially saving you from all the losses you would have had to face due to expired goods.</p><ul><li><strong>Managing data:</strong></li></ul><p>When you are running a business you will always find yourself in the need of viewing your inventory in the various hierarchy. You will also want to break down this contracted stock further at different levels. You can define as many views and labels of the hierarchy as you want and also change them very easily at any point in time. This store inventory management software package offers you high-end analytical tools to look at the consolidation of your stock in many various ways in which.</p><ul><li><strong>Billing Integration:</strong></li></ul><p>In your business, you may need to keep your products at a third party outlet for display and possible sale without actually billing the third party outlet. Since you have not sold the goods to the third party outlet yet, the inventory still belongs to you and you need to keep track of it. .This billing software will adjust the stock at this customer location rather than at your default location automatically whenever you raise an invoice for this customer.</p><ul><li><strong>Automation of reordering:</strong></li></ul><p>The success of your retail business depends upon the correct use of your funds and investments. If you purchase goods that are already in stock and you are not informed about the product that is running out of stock you can lose business both ways. You can specify minimum stock you wish to stay every product at each warehouse.</p><p>So for maintaining the perfect account of your inventory and to manage them use&nbsp;Sompod the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mysoftheaven.com/service/blockchain-technology\"><i><strong>Best Store Management system.</strong></i></a>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong> Inventory management System contains following features:</strong></p><ol><li>Setup</li><li>Order and Issue</li><li>Reports</li><li>Maintenance</li></ol>', '<ol><li>Setup: Enables user to enter details information of the below listed functions. All information regarding establishment of the Inventory management system is provided in this section.</li></ol><ul><li>Category</li><li>Sub Category</li><li>Reference No.</li><li>Option</li><li>Labdip Reference No</li><li>Unit</li><li>Item</li><li>Supplier Information</li><li>Issue To</li></ul><ol><li>Oreder and Issue: Enables user to enter the below listed functions.</li></ol><ul><li>Raw Material Requirement</li><li>PO(Dyeing Order)</li><li>PO(Style Related)</li><li>PO(Common)</li><li>Receive Item(Yarn and Style Related)</li><li>Receive Item(Common)</li><li>Issue Item(Yarn and Style Related)</li><li>Issue Item(Common)</li><li>Receive Finished Goods</li></ul><ol><li>Reports: Enables user to view the below listed functions.</li></ol><ul><li>Date , PO and Style Wise Reports</li><li>Item and Finished Goods wise Reports</li></ul><ol><li>Maintenance:&nbsp; Enables user to create database backup and allow database&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; maintenance and add user from this function.&nbsp;</li></ol>', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '8', 'SMART Inventory, inventory management, mysoft inventory, Best Inventory management tools, Best Inventory management Software in Dhaka, Best Store Management system.', 'Sompod | A complete Inventory/Best Store Management system for managing your inventory product and also things of your store brought by  Mysoftheaven BD Ltd. ', 'http://173.212.223.213/inventory_management/login/generate_token', 30, 1, 1),
(9, '', 'HR Master (এইচআর মাস্টার) |  HR Management system.', 'hr-master', 'HR_Master.png', '<p>HR Master is the complete HR Management system for employee management and consultancy in Bangladesh by Mysoftheaven BD Ltd.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>HR Master (HRMS) Software</strong></p><p>HR master is a Human Resource (HR) software of Bangladesh associated with employee management. Management consultants use their business skills to provide expert advice for improving their performance by resolving a problem. These kinds of problematic issue solver software are HR Master developed by Mysoftheaven (BD) Ltd.</p><p>Business always needs a better product that’s why they need a great team of employees is to have an effective HR department with the right people who motivate them to work hard for the company, fulfill employee demand and concern about officiary satisfaction. Software products to collect and manage the information and centralized the data of every employee in a row which is used for the HR department. The manual system has many hassles to maintain individual documents of attendance, recruitment, bonus, training, service, performance and payroll. HR master gathers all the individuals into one robust package and takes the headache of the HR department as well as business.</p><p><strong>Why do you need to use the HR Master?</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Improve your HR department efficiency:</strong></li></ul><p>The software will help to improve administrative efficiencies in the way the HR manager’s daily tasks and even more productive with less effort. HR software can help you slick your workflow with self-data capture, update employee information and willingness can be developed to all employees.</p><ul><li><strong>Enhance internal communication:</strong></li></ul><p>HR software work as a network where the report, analytics, and tools are shareable to the work team and senior staff members. The business takes a rapid decision on an emergency basis. You are living in a smart edge, you don’t need to hang notice board all the time. So, if you need to send an important message or email to all staff members on their smartphone then you would do with HR software.</p><ul><li><strong>Minimize business cost:</strong></li></ul><p>HR software will support you to reduce administrative costs. When a business investing in a system may they don’t need to hire another administrator and the costs associated with recruitment fees, benefits, salary will save automatically. Manually, the ratio is 1 HR worker against 100 employees to manage data but after install HR Master you can support 1000 employees as well. The software service cost is less than 10 employee salary and recruitment system. In this way, you can save your money because of every single money valuable for business.</p><ul><li><strong>Monitoring employee data:</strong></li></ul><p>The large business needs to handle massive data of employees. Tracking and analyzing is a vital element for effective HR division to control absence, shift manage, leave setup and company property cost analysis. You can get all of this required thing in one system by using HR software.</p><ul><li><strong>Help to the decision-making process:</strong></li></ul><p>When you have all the accurate information in one place, it also helps you to make a better decision for your business growth and analytics. There is no fear of lost your single document because this software has a backup system that always keeps your data safe and refreshes your mind to take the big decision.</p><ul><li><strong>Saving time improve productivity:</strong></li></ul><p>Every company has in time and out time which is fixed. If you follow a manual system with attendance record keeping then it takes more time to execute the whole procedure, instead of this, you can use a fingerprint time clock or punch card time machine which is time-consuming and without hassle. This attendance report saves in the HR software. If your employee will start work at the right time and hassle-free procedure increase your productivity level.</p><ul><li><strong>The facility of payroll management:</strong></li></ul><p>Payroll is an important part of the HR department that’s why software includes topics of payroll. It can save labor dollars, eliminate errors and avoid compliance issues. In this way, these HR Master stores, tracks and calculate employee compensation and deductions. Each employee salary sheet, bonus calculation, pay type and work hours are stored in the system. You can get net income to deduct expenses like local taxes, insurance and retirement savings from gross income.</p><p><strong>Why choose us?</strong></p><ul><li>We delivered HR Master 80+ company in Bangladesh and they are satisfied with our services. Their satisfaction level is 99% because we keep our promise to give the best service.</li><li>Providing the latest technology and upgrade version of HR Master. We will give a 3-month free service after buying our software.</li><li>We take your HR headache, for this reason, we complete all software setup and for the user, we give a special free training session.</li><li>We use the excellent server for backup your all information.</li><li>24/7 support system and provide secured management whereas we know your information is valuable for your business.</li></ul><p>For the completes <a href=\"http://mysoftheaven.com/service/manpower-outsource\"><i><strong>HR Management system</strong></i></a> for employee management and consultancy in Bangladesh contact with Mysoftheaven BD Ltd.&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Presentation Layer</th><td>JAVA, PHP, AJAX,HTML4, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap</td></tr><tr><th>Distributed Services</th><td>Web service</td></tr><tr><th>Application Layer</th><td>Windows workflow foundation</td></tr><tr><th>Domain/Business Model Layer</th><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><th>Persistence/Access Layer</th><td>Domain Data Model</td></tr><tr><th>Operating System</th><td>Windows, Linux</td></tr><tr><th>Web Application Sever</th><td>Apache</td></tr><tr><th>IDE</th><td>Sublime Text</td></tr><tr><th>Reporting</th><td>PHP Reporting</td></tr><tr><th>Framework</th><td>Codeigniter, CakePHP</td></tr><tr><th>Mobile Apps development</th><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>', '45', 'HR Master, HR Master Programs, HR Master data, HR solution companies, hr solutions bd, hr management system project,', 'HR Master is the complete HR Management system for employee management and consultancy in Bangladesh by Mysoftheaven BD Ltd. ', NULL, 80, 1, 1);
